---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us - BoardTools"
  description="Learn about the mission, philosophy, and local-first security of BoardTools, the visual workspace for web utilities."
>
  <section class="max-w-[1280px] w-full mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-12 flex flex-col gap-10 animate-fade-in-up">
    <!-- Breadcrumb & Header -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate uppercase">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-primary">Home</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span class="text-brand-blue">About Us</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-display font-medium text-4xl sm:text-5xl tracking-tight text-primary mt-1">
        About BoardTools
      </h1>
      <p class="text-base text-slate max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        We believe that developer and designer utility tools don't have to be clinical, boring, or insecure. BoardTools reimagines single-purpose converters and checkers as a tactile, collaborative visual playground.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Grid Content -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
      <!-- Left Content Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col gap-8">
        <div class="card-base flex flex-col gap-4">
          <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-xl text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow"></span>
            Our Philosophy: Local-First Security
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate leading-relaxed">
            Every day, developers paste API tokens, database JSON rows, sensitive URLs, and personal UUIDs into online converters. Most of these sites upload your text to server backends, logging them or running tracking codes.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate leading-relaxed font-semibold">
            BoardTools is different. It is 100% serverless.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate leading-relaxed">
            All algorithms—from base64 decoding to JSON format validation—run locally inside your browser's V8 sandbox. Zero bytes of your input data are ever transmitted to our servers. Your security is guaranteed by design, not just by a privacy policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="card-base flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-teal-light text-moss-dark flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm select-none">⚡</div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-base text-primary">Microsecond Execution</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate leading-relaxed">
              Without roundtrips to servers, conversions happen instantly as you type. Real-time feedback lines guide you to JSON syntax errors immediately.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card-base flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-rose-light text-primary flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm select-none">🎨</div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-base text-primary">Miro-Inspired Canvas</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate leading-relaxed">
              Visual sketching and draggable sticky notes let you brainstorm interfaces, map flows, and keep raw text notes side-by-side with formatters.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Feature Column (Pastel Card Accent) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="card-feature-yellow flex flex-col gap-6">
          <span class="badge-tag-yellow bg-yellow-light text-yellow-dark self-start">THE MISSION</span>
          <h2 class="font-display font-medium text-2xl tracking-tight text-primary">
            Bridging the gap between structure and visual design.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-yellow-dark/95 leading-relaxed">
            Web development is visual. Designer handoffs, responsive grids, and API integrations require builders to jump between text formats and layout drawings. 
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-yellow-dark/95 leading-relaxed">
            BoardTools gathers these disparate workflows into a single workspace, giving teams the exact utilities they need alongside a canvas to organize their thoughts.
          </p>
          <div class="h-[1px] bg-yellow-dark/20 my-2"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-yellow-light border border-yellow-dark/20 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm text-yellow-dark select-none font-display">B</div>
            <div class="flex flex-col">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-primary">BoardTools Core Team</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] text-yellow-dark/80 font-medium">Built with Astro & Tailwind 4</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Milestones/Timeline section -->
    <div class="card-base bg-surface-soft flex flex-col gap-6">
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-primary text-center">Core Project Milestones</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 relative">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 p-4 bg-canvas rounded-xl border border-hairline">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-blue uppercase">Phase 1 &bull; Core Utilities</span>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-sm text-primary">Local Code Sandboxing</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate leading-relaxed">
            Established client-only formatting engines for JSON parsing, UUID token generation, and Base64 translations safely.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 p-4 bg-canvas rounded-xl border border-hairline">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-teal uppercase">Phase 2 &bull; Canvas Flow</span>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-sm text-primary">Interactive Drawing</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate leading-relaxed">
            Integrated mouse and touch pen sketchpads with HTML5 canvas, introducing sticky notes and local storage saving.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 p-4 bg-canvas rounded-xl border border-hairline">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-coral uppercase">Phase 3 &bull; Dark Mode & Beyond</span>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-sm text-primary">Refined Theme Aesthetics</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate leading-relaxed">
            Adopted Tailwind CSS v4 design parameters. Delivered seamless dark mode swaps, accessible contrast ratings, and dynamic reviews.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
